short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: MovingLake's Chrome Extension helps you authorize connectors faster and simpler

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MovingLake's Chrome Extension helps you authorize connectors faster and simpler by accessing your session's cookies and pushing them to the configuration of the connector.

No cookie will be sent unless you purposefully click the button to refresh the cookie in our servers.
